Question: One room has turquoise-blue bookshelves with square compartments, and the other room shows a head-on light-colored bookcase wall that is completely filled with books.

Reference Answer: True

Right image URL: https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/70/47/a7/7047a72058d201c44eaae9e3d8b1efd9.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a room with turquoise-blue bookshelves with square compartments?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a room with turquoise-blue bookshelves with square compartments?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a room with a head-on light-colored bookcase wall?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a room with a head-on light-colored bookcase wall?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the bookcase wall completely filled with books?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the bookcase wall completely filled with books?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} xor {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
